{"tid":711394,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] ガーディアンズ Guardians 守護者 (4) too many sorcerers","createTime":"2018-06-21T13:20:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T22:29:51.000Z","uid":17776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3bc843acbc9354faa4200115731d9600bb53cd8d","tid":711394,"uid":17776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T13:20:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/06/200828_7d22d32a98183e1846cb33db3d9dae70.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F06%2F200828_7d22d32a98183e1846cb33db3d9dae70.png&h=9d40bee4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nios <a href=\"https://t.co/WzznbxDTao?amp=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FWzznbxDTao%3Famp%3D1&d=whoAJaSLdZX72J61Z%2FbMTcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=c9acbcc6\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.co/WzznbxDTao?amp=1</a><br />\n<br />\nan <a href=\"https://t.co/dGcQQtrePd?amp=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FdGcQQtrePd%3Famp%3D1&d=whoAJaSLdZX72J61Z%2FbMTcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=0b26e24b\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.co/dGcQQtrePd?amp=1</a><br />\n<br />\n係好舊式既 mmorpg<br />\n<br />\n打怪升lvl，轉職，強化<br />\n<br />\n可以組隊打任務，似mon hunt<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/06/200856_4e904acf27cfe3031130948dc075f5e2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F06%2F200856_4e904acf27cfe3031130948dc075f5e2.png&h=30f2f441&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/06/200856_b7bdbbcef0f6efcf870fe1eb565403b6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F06%2F200856_b7bdbbcef0f6efcf870fe1eb565403b6.png&h=483dddbe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/06/200857_b7bdbbcef0f6efcf870fe1eb565403b6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F06%2F200857_b7bdbbcef0f6efcf870fe1eb565403b6.png&h=a02a4d1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n職業<br />\n<br />\n基本職業分四種<br />\n<br />\n1. 劍士<br />\n<br />\n攻防重點<br />\n<br />\n【装備可能】剣、大剣、盾、鎧、兜、サークレット<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 遊俠<br />\n<br />\n遠程攻擊<br />\n物理攻擊和狀態異常的技能。<br />\n防禦力低<br />\n<br />\n【装備可能】斧、弓、 サークレット、軽装、ハット<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 魔法師<br />\n<br />\n以魔法攻擊為中心<br />\n魔力高<br />\n<br />\n由於防禦力低，不擅長接近戰鬥<br />\n<br />\n火，水，風和地屬性攻擊魔法<br />\n<br />\n【装備可能】杖、ハット、ローブ、サークレット<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4. 牧師<br />\n<br />\n恢復魔法<br />\n<br />\n攻擊力和防禦力很低，支持其他職業為主<br />\n<br />\n【装備可能】槍、杖、盾、法衣、ローブ、サークレット<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上位職業<br />\n<br />\n升基本職業LV並滿足條件，可以轉移到上級職位。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n◆Gladiator <br />\n條件：劍士LV 30<br />\n<br />\n◆騎士<br />\n條件：劍士 LV 20&middot;牧師LV 20<br />\n<br />\n◆Rogue<br />\n條件：遊俠LV 20&middot;魔法LV 20<br />\n<br />\n◆狙擊手<br />\n條件：遊俠LV 30<br />\n<br />\n◆主教<br />\n條件：牧師LV 30<br />\n<br />\n◆巫師<br />\n條件：魔法LV 30<br />\n<br />\n◆聖人<br />\n條件：牧師LV 20&middot;魔法LV 20<br />\n<br />\n*轉職後會變為1LV 如果弓轉法/戰 等等要小心裝備唔通用<br />\n<br />\n裝備<br />\n有ssr武器就開得<br />\n其他裝備遲下係可以升上ssr<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/06/202632_022316a5d7672282857e16a51d0b0661.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F06%2F202632_022316a5d7672282857e16a51d0b0661.png&h=2b9a5b92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n右上入珠<br />\n右下入後備裝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n經驗值 想快既<br />\n1. 大地圖 組隊 <br />\n2. 打 兔仔<br />\n3. 食野 300鑽換一張飛 30分鐘雙經<br />\n4. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">玩法師</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好友<br />\n442 578 102 - Ball"},{"pid":"c348ed8c6c6c1bab870b8eb558d6ce3139a4804d","tid":711394,"uid":17776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T13:21:59.000Z","msg":"1001 ?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"785e89d4a93cd590b64382874018e75d0db1eb11","tid":711394,"uid":188257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T17:33:21.000Z","msg":"更新得好慢，D職又唔平衡<br />\n<br />\n唔知堅持到幾耐唔棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2187e2991e9ba3c569f284f3c360e5ff6d32c9c","tid":711394,"uid":30262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T18:08:11.000Z","msg":"夜晚D GR4組隊愈來愈少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c4edfe933d27b26329f83a16b58749809b3d43","tid":711394,"uid":17065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2187e2991e9ba3c569f284f3c360e5ff6d32c9c","tid":711394,"uid":30262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T18:08:11.000Z","msg":"夜晚D GR4組隊愈來愈少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T18:21:50.000Z","msg":"到無人打兔既時侯 呢隻game就係執得喇"},{"pid":"8a8f7d745733fd8d1da23304da8c16838c7b30f8","tid":711394,"uid":133875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T18:21:51.000Z","msg":"聽晚修bug 12-3am"},{"pid":"827fa51942077640be298da90b562feeaf16b757","tid":711394,"uid":17776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T22:29:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/711399/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/711399/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n集中入呢個post傾<br />\n<br />\n開左兩個"}]}